<div class="page-desc">
    <div class="enc365-page-title">账户绑定</div>
    登录您的环智中诚™账户, 并将此 Encryption365 客户端注册到您的账户名下, 即刻开始管理和自动化部署、续费您的 SSL 安全证书。
</div>
{# 登录框 #}
<div style="max-width: 360px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 85px;">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; border: 2px solid #20a53a; line-height: 50px; border-radius: 30px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," style="height: 35px;">
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px;margin-bottom: 15px;">登陆您的 <strong>环智中诚™</strong> 账户, 并关联此客户端。</p>
    </div>
    <form id="loginForm">
    <div class="line">
        <span class="tname">账户邮箱</span>
        <input class="bt-input-text" id="to_username" name="username" required type="email" placeholder="my@example.com" value="" style="width: 230px;">
    </div>
    <div class="line">
        <span class="tname">账户密码</span>
        <input class="bt-input-text" id="to_password" name="password" required type="password" value="" style="width: 230px;">
    </div>
    <div class="line" style="padding-left: 100px;">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-sm" title="立即登录并在环智中诚™账户内注册和绑定此客户端"> 登录并绑定</button>
    </div>
    <div class="line" style="padding-left: 100px;">
        <a href="javascript:;" onclick="javascript:encryption365.page('getRegister');" title="点此按钮免费注册并获得 环智中诚™ 账户"> 免费注册 环智中诚™ 账户?</a>
    </div>
    </form>
</div>
<script>
    $('form#loginForm').submit(function(e){
        e.preventDefault(); // 禁止常规提交
        encryption365.clientRegister($('#to_username').val(), $('#to_password').val());
    });
</script>